data.description: Note, this is a high-end Horton Series home, not a Traditions Series which are also built in Silverado.  All Appliances included with a Full Price Offer Fully Executed on or before 1-31-2024.  Like New 1 Yr Old, Smart Home, Full Brick, Gutters, Fireplace, Wood-Look Ceramic Tile perfect for pets and children, Carpet in BRs, Energy Efficient, Tankless HWH, Programmable Sprinklers front to back with rain sensor, Easy to Clean Lean-In Windows, Epoxy Garage Flooring, Impeccable Lawn and Flower Beds, Spacious Primary Bath with Double Sinks, Garden Tub and Separate Shower, a Secondary Bath with Double Sinks and Double Cabinetry to accommodate space and storage for multiple users, Covered Back Patio, Ceiling Fans and 2 Inch Blinds throughout, SS Gas Cooktop and Convection Combo, and SS Microwave vents to the outside. Silverado is Rated No.6 in US and No.1 in TX by RCLCO with its Country Club Resort Style Living, including Pickleball and Live Lifeguards during pool hours. This is a Must See!
